{
  "stem": "1160.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like a mirror which has two, like, night tables.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It looked like a night tables-- two side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you could open the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, it had-- and the mirror was coming out high.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Quite high.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then, the mirror, you could close it in like a book.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, between these two cupboards-- little night tables, I should say-- like a little shelf and a little drawer to pull out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was very pretty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I liked to sit on it, look myself in the-- and I just was imagining and playing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was my mother's.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my mother went, walked out to almost-- quite far from the-- a distance she had to walk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She walked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She never knew those people before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when she went there, and we're all excited that we are going to get back something of ours.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Time passes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she comes back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She's walking slow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She is crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She is crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we ask, what's the matter?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Why are you crying?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What's wrong?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, don't anybody ever tell me that you find something of mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't care who has it, I don't want it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not going to go for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- and she could hardly talk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was sobbing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It-- she could hardly talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just awful to see this mother cry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, she says to us, when this woman opened-- this Hungarian woman opened the door, and she says, what do you want?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she says, well, I'm so and so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- you have my piece.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother says, when she was opening the door, this woman-- she saw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She saw the furniture a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's there.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
